        <name>keep_section_info</name>
        <qualifiedname>llext_load_param::keep_section_info</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Keep the ELF section data in memory after loading the extension. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This is needed to use some of the functions in <ref refid="group__llext__inspect__apis" kindref="compound">ELF inspection APIs</ref>.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>Related memory must be freed by <ref refid="group__llext__apis_1ga54f3aaed749e8c6bad6fbecb1622ab06" kindref="member">llext_free_inspection_data</ref> before the extension can be unloaded via <ref refid="group__llext__apis_1gad3df7ed4d436846504c0047166eb929e" kindref="member">llext_unload</ref>. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
